****Build NGM:****

Required software:
cmake
zlib (Ubuntu: zlib1g-dev)
cudatoolkit


1) Build MASon:

wget http://www.cibiv.at/software/ngm/mason/download/mason-src-08_17_2012.tar.gz
tar xfvz mason-src-08_17_2012.tar.gz
cd mason-trunk
mkdir -p build/release
cd build/release/
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ../..
make
make install (root required)

If you don't have root permissions, please add the path to the MASon libs to yout LD_LIBRARY_PATH:

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=<mason path>

After building you find the compiled libraries in the "mason-trunk/bin" folder.


2) Build NGM:

wget http://www.cibiv.at/software/ngm/NGM/download/ngm-src-08_17_2012.tar.gz
tar xvfz ngm-src-08_17_2012.tar.gz
cd ngm-trunk
mkdir -p build/release
cd build/release/
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ../..
make

cd ../../bin
./NGM

